{"tid":686973,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"奧地利商店洩露《DMC 5》 年內登陸Xbox One/PS4","createTime":"2018-06-01T19:11:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-11T02:11:24.000Z","uid":66943,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b51a5c865851c294df8f171da6ffc06f1700f338","tid":686973,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T19:11:47.000Z","msg":"日前奧地利電商Gameware上架了《鬼泣5 》遊戲。<br />\n<img src=\"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2018/06/20180601_cyl_36_3/gamersky_01origin_01_201861847F2A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg1.gamersky.com%2Fimage2018%2F06%2F20180601_cyl_36_3%2Fgamersky_01origin_01_201861847F2A.jpg&h=b67deb91&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n根據Gameware信息顯示，《鬼泣5》預定2018年內登陸Xbox One，PS4平台，售價約為70歐元。雖然沒有PC平台，不過根據著名論壇 Resetera網友爆料的情報，該作的PC版比主機版較晚發布，而且遊戲將採用Unreal Engine 4引擎開發，之前Capcom也表示將會聚焦他們的知名系列新作。"},{"pid":"1118ce1e3faec6453ca8b3e3df94b6c62f13fcc6","tid":686973,"uid":23549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T05:26:09.000Z","msg":"70歐元<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n4a級作品<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47722330b64b067410272b30e357c3272b7db0e0","tid":686973,"uid":153318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T01:26:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.capcom.co.jp/devil5/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.capcom.co.jp%2Fdevil5%2F&d=F49045if5U1yo1pgcUX29bIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=a75a9ebd\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.capcom.co.jp/devil5/</a>"},{"pid":"7d07fcf7114a972e175d7061bc539ca08c6ac5df","tid":686973,"uid":64598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T01:32:18.000Z","msg":"嗰個係Nero來？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df34dc9eab57a14d0089d2e293ca52261d4101ef"